{
  "stem": "24268.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was I and my sister and the three of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So the German looked at us and he said [GERMAN], [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We didn't know what [GERMAN] meant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We didn't know that was the start of the whole knowledge, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We didn't know one was to go back home.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We had a-- still have the home yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And the two was evidently left there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "We found out was sent to camp, to forced labor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And everything was forced labor, whatever I did, even being home, sort of.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So and the third was to [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That means to liquidation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we then-- we came later on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We heard crying, and people cried.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We didn't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And our cousins, who helped us to get into the [INAUDIBLE], he himself with the whole family got number three, for destruction, completely, for the Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The youngest remain, that he wanted to [GERMAN], that means he wanted to-- he wanted himself to get to the parents.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He didn't want to stay alone by himself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "He was very heartbroken, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And-- but we-- Mom said, don't go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "As long as you going to be outside, maybe we can still do something for you-- for the family.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Which he did listen, and he paid off someone later on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "See, they gather the people, whoever they had, supposed to send away to Auschwitz, for the-- which they probably, you know, they-- they knew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "So then they-- he tried-- they gathered in one place, and that I think was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "That was all the people, before they sent to camp, they send them to this building, which they-- wherever they could, whoever they grab who are on their way before they send it out.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
